Perl6::Pod
=====================

Perl6::Pod - use Perl6's pod in perl5 programms


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Regexp::Grammars

SEE ALSO

Podlite is a lightweight block-based markup language designed for flexibility and ease of use.

Podlite represents the evolution of Synopsis26 ideas.
Follow Podlite news and developments:

  * Podlite Perl module (https://metacpan.org/release/Podlite)
    Podlite support for Perl on CPAN

  * Podlite Specification (https://podlite.org/specification)
    Official specification in HTML

  * Podlite Specification Source (https://github.com/podlite/podlite-specs)
    Specification source code

  * podlite.org (https://podlite.org)
    Official website

